oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: David Houston at the Farm Festival Building (16316)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houston, David, 1937-; Tabuchi, Shoji; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on light brown) announcing David Houston with Shoji Tabuchi, Calvin Crawford, and the Persuaders Band at the Farm Festival Building in Tioga, North Dakota on April 12. Poster features metal photoplates of David Houston, Shoji Tabuchi, and Calvin Crawford. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/40675.
